about:
Hi, I'm JKawesome, but most people call me JK. I'm one of the best rushers in Nebula currently on the server. I've learned a variety of tricks to getting monuments on almost every map.

I do have a server, but it's multi-purpose, for scrims, build, etc, but I'm not going to advertise. So If you want to build on it or something, add me on Skype. Also, check out my Youtube channel for monument tips and montage videos here :D



Best achievements in Nebula:

? Crafted 2 beacons in one Rendezvous game

? Broken a monument with my fist

? Broken a monument without placing/breaking any blocks

? Ended a Quintus match 5 minutes after it started

? Ended a Senex match 2 minutes after it started

? Broken 15 monuments in a row

? Breached a defense where the monument was on a glass platform, and about 10 diamond defenders on the platform
